entry.npcText: Hey new roommate, we're moving in this weekend! You excited??
entry.playerText: Hell yeah! Its gonna be great!

entry.npcText: Its crazy, moving into a new place, but its gonna be awesome. :D I may not be here when you get here, I be at a party
entry.playerText: That's cool, means I'll be able to get a hang of things while you're out.

entry.npcText: Cool!! I'm super excited :D
OH, I FORGOT TO TELL YOU. I hooked us up a nice 42" TV up in our common space. :D
HELL YEAH ITS 1080p! It'll be sweet :D our pad will be a party pad!
entry.playerText: Sweeeeet. I am excite for move in tomorrow.

entry.npcText: THERE IS ALSO A FRIDGE. BOOM. WE HAVE THE ABILITY TO CHILL THINGS!
Talk to you later! I gotta go take care of some things for the party tomorrow.
